name: .ENPASSBACKUP
summary: Learn about .ENPASSBACKUP files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

instructions: You can only open ENPASSBACKUP files with Sinew Enpass (cross-platform). To open an ENPASSBACKUP file and restore its contents, select This PC from the home screen and select Backup File (you must enter the master password to open the file).
